summary: Adds a Spell based merchant to Whiterun behind Apothecary.
descriptionHtml:
[size=6]Ragnars Spell Booth[/size]



Adds a Spell based merchant to Whiterun behind Apothecary. Also adds 5 dummys to White run; 3 on Guard House and 2 Near booth to test your spells you bought and see how they work if you are unfamiliar with them.


Spell Merchants Name is Ragnar Vonweazel. He is a High Elf who was banished from the Thalmor for aiding the Stormcloaks. He still wears his pride and joy, the Thalmor Robes. He is fully equipped to deal with any trouble you might decide to give him. He is also set to essential so Civil War and other events like that cannot harm him.
author: Tcthetitan65
